N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 205.11 - Identification of regional fire administrator

State Regulations

The bureau of fire mobilization and control shall issue the
following appointment certificate and identification card to regional fire
administrators: (a) Appointment
certificate. Image
(b) Identification card. Image
